Use the sttibute stye coloe size and get item id (LKP_ITEM_2)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DAY_DIMENSION.V_CURRENTMONTH as V_CURRENTMONTH, DAY_DIMENSION.V_CURYR as V_CURYR, DAY_DIMENSION.V_P2_Month as V_P2_Month, DAY_DIMENSION.V_P2_YR as V_P2_YR, DAY_DIMENSION.V_P1_Month as V_P1_Month, DAY_DIMENSION.V_P1_YR as V_P1_YR, DAY_DIMENSION.DUMMY as DUMMY FROM (select CY_MONTH_NUM as V_CurrentMonth , TO_NUMBER(CY_YEAR_YYYY) as V_CURYR, CASE WHEN CY_MONTH_NUM - 2 <= 0 THEN ((12 + TO_NUMBER(CY_MONTH_NUM)) - 2 ) ELSE TO_NUMBER(CY_MONTH_NUM) -2 END as V_P2_Month , CASE WHEN CY_MONTH_NUM - 2 <= 0 THEN CY_YEAR_YYYY-1 ELSE TO_NUMBER(CY_YEAR_YYYY) END as V_P2_YR , CASE WHEN ( TO_NUMBER(CY_MONTH_NUM)-1) = 0 THEN 12 ELSE TO_NUMBER(CY_MONTH_NUM) - 1 END as V_P1_Month, CASE WHEN CY_MONTH_NUM - 1 = 0 THEN TO_NUMBER(CY_YEAR_YYYY)-1 ELSE to_number(CY_YEAR_YYYY) END as V_P1_YR, 1 as DUMMY from day_dimension where day_date = (SELECT (AS_OF_DATE - 7) FROM DAY_DIMENSION d WHERE DAY_DATE = TRUNC(SYSDATE) ))DAY_DIMENSION

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DAY_DIMENSION.V_PREVWK as V_PREVWK, DAY_DIMENSION.V_CurrMonth as V_CurrMonth, DAY_DIMENSION.DUMMY as DUMMY FROM (select distinct TO_NUMBER(cy_wk_of_month) as V_Prevwk, TO_NUMBER(CY_MONTH_NUM) as V_CurrMonth, 1 as DUMMY from day_dimension where day_date = (SELECT (AS_OF_DATE - 7) FROM DAY_DIMENSION d WHERE DAY_DATE = TRUNC(SYSDATE))) DAY_DIMENSION

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: get MAX period, year
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_MAX_PD_YR

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DAY_DIMENSION.V_MAX_YR as V_MAX_YR, DAY_DIMENSION.V_MAX_PD as V_MAX_PD, DAY_DIMENSION.DUMMY as DUMMY FROM ( select max(cy_year_yyyy) AS v_max_yr, max(cy_month_num) AS v_max_pd ,1 as dummy from day_dimension where as_of_date = (select max(TRUNC(as_of_date)) + 28 from day_dimension where cy_wk_of_year = ( select max(to_number(cy_wk_of_year)) from day_dimension where as_of_date = (SELECT (AS_OF_DATE - 7) FROM DAY_DIMENSION d WHERE DAY_DATE = TRUNC(SYSDATE) ) ) and cy_year_yyyy = ( select max(cy_year_yyyy) - 1 from day_dimension where as_of_date = (SELECT (AS_OF_DATE - 7) FROM DAY_DIMENSION d WHERE DAY_DATE = TRUNC(SYSDATE) ) ))) DAY_DIMENSION

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: get mininmum period, year, as_of_date and MAX(AS_OF_DATE)
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_MIN_PD_YR

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DAY_DIMENSION.V_MIN_PD as V_MIN_PD, DAY_DIMENSION.V_MIN_YR as V_MIN_YR, DAY_DIMENSION.V_MIN_AOD as V_MIN_AOD, DAY_DIMENSION.V_MAX_AOD as V_MAX_AOD, DAY_DIMENSION.DUMMY as DUMMY FROM (select min(cy_month_num) AS v_min_pd, min(cy_year_yyyy) AS v_min_yr, min(TRUNC(as_of_date)) AS v_min_AOD, (max(TRUNC(as_of_date)) + 28) as v_max_AOD , 1 as dummy from day_dimension where cy_wk_of_year = ( select max(to_number(cy_wk_of_year)) from day_dimension where as_of_date = (SELECT (AS_OF_DATE - 7) FROM DAY_DIMENSION d WHERE DAY_DATE = TRUNC(SYSDATE) ) ) and cy_year_yyyy = ( select max(cy_year_yyyy) - 1 from day_dimension where as_of_date = (SELECT (AS_OF_DATE - 7) FROM DAY_DIMENSION d WHERE DAY_DATE = TRUNC(SYSDATE) ) ))DAY_DIMENSION

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: to get V_last_P6_Month V_last_P6_Yr V_last_YR
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_LASTYEAR

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select DAY_DIMENSION.V_last_YR as V_last_YR,DAY_DIMENSION.V_last_P6_Month as V_last_P6_Month,DAY_DIMENSION.V_last_P6_Yr as V_last_P6_Yr,DAY_DIMENSION.DUMMY as DUMMY from (select CY_YEAR_YYYY-1 as V_last_YR,CASE WHEN CY_MONTH_NUM - 6 <= 0 THEN ((12 + TO_NUMBER(CY_MONTH_NUM)) - 6 ) ELSE TO_NUMBER(CY_MONTH_NUM) -6 END as V_last_P6_Month,CASE WHEN CY_MONTH_NUM - 6 <= 0 THEN CY_YEAR_YYYY-1 ELSE TO_NUMBER(CY_YEAR_YYYY) END as V_last_P6_Yr,1 as DUMMY from day_dimension where day_date = (SELECT (AS_OF_DATE - 7) FROM DAY_DIMENSION d WHERE DAY_DATE = TRUNC(SYSDATE) ))DAY_DIMENSION

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: look up on day dimension
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_DAY_DIMENSION

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select a.DAY_DATE as DAY_DATE, d60.AS_OF_DATE as v_BEGIN_60, a.AS_OF_DATE as V_END_60, d180.AS_OF_DATE as V_BEGIN_180, a.AS_OF_DATE as V_END_180, d360.AS_OF_DATE as V_BEGIN_360, a.AS_OF_DATE as V_END_360 from slba.day_dimension a left join slba.day_dimension d60 on a.AS_OF_DATE-60 = d60.DAY_DATE left join slba.day_dimension d180 on a.AS_OF_DATE-180 = d180.DAY_DATE left join slba.day_dimension d360 on a.AS_OF_DATE-360 = d360.DAY_DATE
